{"snp1.3:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 1.3 ","snp1.3:0.2":"Khaggavisanasutta ","snp1.3:1.1":"“Sabbesu bhutesu nidhaya dandam, ","snp1.3:1.2":"Avihethayam annatarampi tesam; ","snp1.3:1.3":"Na puttamiccheyya kuto sahayam, ","snp1.3:1.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:2.1":"“Samsaggajatassa bhavanti sneha, ","snp1.3:2.2":"Snehanvayam dukkhamidam pahoti; ","snp1.3:2.3":"Adinavam snehajam pekkhamano, ","snp1.3:2.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:3.1":"“Mitte suhajje anukampamano, ","snp1.3:3.2":"Hapeti attham patibaddhacitto; ","snp1.3:3.3":"Etam bhayam santhave pekkhamano, ","snp1.3:3.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:4.1":"“Vamso visalova yatha visatto, ","snp1.3:4.2":"Puttesu daresu ca ya apekkha; ","snp1.3:4.3":"Vamsakkalirova asajjamano, ","snp1.3:4.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:5.1":"“Migo arannamhi yatha abaddho, ","snp1.3:5.2":"Yenicchakam gacchati gocaraya; ","snp1.3:5.3":"Vinnu naro seritam pekkhamano, ","snp1.3:5.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:6.1":"“Amantana hoti sahayamajjhe, ","snp1.3:6.2":"Vase thane gamane carikaya; ","snp1.3:6.3":"Anabhijjhitam seritam pekkhamano, ","snp1.3:6.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:7.1":"“Khidda rati hoti sahayamajjhe, ","snp1.3:7.2":"Puttesu ca vipulam hoti pemam; ","snp1.3:7.3":"Piyavippayogam vijigucchamano, ","snp1.3:7.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:8.1":"“Catuddiso appatigho ca hoti, ","snp1.3:8.2":"Santussamano itaritarena; ","snp1.3:8.3":"Parissayanam sahita achambhi, ","snp1.3:8.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:9.1":"“Dussangaha pabbajitapi eke, ","snp1.3:9.2":"Atho gahattha gharamavasanta; ","snp1.3:9.3":"Appossukko paraputtesu hutva, ","snp1.3:9.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:10.1":"“Oropayitva gihibyanjanani, ","snp1.3:10.2":"Sanchinnapatto yatha kovilaro; ","snp1.3:10.3":"Chetvana viro gihibandhanani, ","snp1.3:10.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:11.1":"“Sace labhetha nipakam sahayam, ","snp1.3:11.2":"Saddhim caram sadhuviharidhiram; ","snp1.3:11.3":"Abhibhuyya sabbani parissayani, ","snp1.3:11.4":"Careyya tenattamano satima”. ","snp1.3:12.1":"“No ce labhetha nipakam sahayam, ","snp1.3:12.2":"Saddhim caram sadhuviharidhiram; ","snp1.3:12.3":"Rajava rattham vijitam pahaya, ","snp1.3:12.4":"Eko care matangaranneva nago”. ","snp1.3:13.1":"“Addha pasamsama sahayasampadam, ","snp1.3:13.2":"Settha sama sevitabba sahaya; ","snp1.3:13.3":"Ete aladdha anavajjabhoji, ","snp1.3:13.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:14.1":"“Disva suvannassa pabhassarani, ","snp1.3:14.2":"Kammaraputtena sunitthitani; ","snp1.3:14.3":"Sanghattamanani duve bhujasmim, ","snp1.3:14.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:15.1":"“Evam dutiyena saha mamassa, ","snp1.3:15.2":"Vacabhilapo abhisajjana va; ","snp1.3:15.3":"Etam bhayam ayatim pekkhamano, ","snp1.3:15.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:16.1":"“Kama hi citra madhura manorama, ","snp1.3:16.2":"Viruparupena mathenti cittam; ","snp1.3:16.3":"Adinavam kamagunesu disva, ","snp1.3:16.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:17.1":"“Iti ca gando ca upaddavo ca, ","snp1.3:17.2":"Rogo ca sallanca bhayanca metam; ","snp1.3:17.3":"Etam bhayam kamagunesu disva, ","snp1.3:17.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:18.1":"“Sitanca unhanca khudam pipasam, ","snp1.3:18.2":"Vatatape damsasarisape ca; ","snp1.3:18.3":"Sabbanipetani abhisambhavitva, ","snp1.3:18.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:19.1":"“Nagova yuthani vivajjayitva, ","snp1.3:19.2":"Sanjatakhandho padumi ularo; ","snp1.3:19.3":"Yathabhirantam viharam aranne, ","snp1.3:19.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:20.1":"“Atthanatam sanganikaratassa, ","snp1.3:20.2":"Yam phassaye samayikam vimuttim; ","snp1.3:20.3":"Adiccabandhussa vaco nisamma, ","snp1.3:20.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:21.1":"“Ditthivisukani upativatto, ","snp1.3:21.2":"Patto niyamam patiladdhamaggo; ","snp1.3:21.3":"Uppannananomhi anannaneyyo, ","snp1.3:21.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:22.1":"“Nillolupo nikkuho nippipaso, ","snp1.3:22.2":"Nimmakkho niddhantakasavamoho; ","snp1.3:22.3":"Nirasayo sabbaloke bhavitva, ","snp1.3:22.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:23.1":"“Papam sahayam parivajjayetha, ","snp1.3:23.2":"Anatthadassim visame nivittham; ","snp1.3:23.3":"Sayam na seve pasutam pamattam, ","snp1.3:23.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:24.1":"“Bahussutam dhammadharam bhajetha, ","snp1.3:24.2":"Mittam ularam patibhanavantam; ","snp1.3:24.3":"Annaya atthani vineyya kankham, ","snp1.3:24.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:25.1":"“Khiddam ratim kamasukhanca loke, ","snp1.3:25.2":"Analankaritva anapekkhamano; ","snp1.3:25.3":"Vibhusanatthana virato saccavadi, ","snp1.3:25.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:26.1":"“Puttanca daram pitaranca mataram, ","snp1.3:26.2":"Dhanani dhannani ca bandhavani; ","snp1.3:26.3":"Hitvana kamani yathodhikani, ","snp1.3:26.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:27.1":"“Sango eso parittamettha sokhyam, ","snp1.3:27.2":"Appassado dukkhamettha bhiyyo; ","snp1.3:27.3":"Galo eso iti natva matima, ","snp1.3:27.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:28.1":"“Sandalayitvana samyojanani, ","snp1.3:28.2":"Jalamva bhetva salilambucari; ","snp1.3:28.3":"Aggiva daddham anivattamano, ","snp1.3:28.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:29.1":"“Okkhittacakkhu na ca padalolo, ","snp1.3:29.2":"Guttindriyo rakkhitamanasano; ","snp1.3:29.3":"Anavassuto aparidayhamano, ","snp1.3:29.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:30.1":"“Oharayitva gihibyanjanani, ","snp1.3:30.2":"Sanchannapatto yatha parichatto; ","snp1.3:30.3":"Kasayavattho abhinikkhamitva, ","snp1.3:30.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:31.1":"“Rasesu gedham akaram alolo, ","snp1.3:31.2":"Anannaposi sapadanacari; ","snp1.3:31.3":"Kule kule appatibaddhacitto, ","snp1.3:31.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:32.1":"“Pahaya pancavaranani cetaso, ","snp1.3:32.2":"Upakkilese byapanujja sabbe; ","snp1.3:32.3":"Anissito chetva sinehadosam, ","snp1.3:32.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:33.1":"“Vipitthikatvana sukham dukhanca, ","snp1.3:33.2":"Pubbeva ca somanassadomanassam; ","snp1.3:33.3":"Laddhanupekkham samatham visuddham, ","snp1.3:33.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:34.1":"“Araddhaviriyo paramatthapattiya, ","snp1.3:34.2":"Alinacitto akusitavutti; ","snp1.3:34.3":"Dalhanikkamo thamabalupapanno, ","snp1.3:34.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:35.1":"“Patisallanam jhanamarincamano, ","snp1.3:35.2":"Dhammesu niccam anudhammacari; ","snp1.3:35.3":"Adinavam sammasita bhavesu, ","snp1.3:35.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:36.1":"“Tanhakkhayam patthayamappamatto, ","snp1.3:36.2":"Anelamugo sutava satima; ","snp1.3:36.3":"Sankhatadhammo niyato padhanava, ","snp1.3:36.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:37.1":"“Sihova saddesu asantasanto, ","snp1.3:37.2":"Vatova jalamhi asajjamano; ","snp1.3:37.3":"Padumamva toyena alippamano, ","snp1.3:37.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:38.1":"“Siho yatha dathabali pasayha, ","snp1.3:38.2":"Raja miganam abhibhuyya cari; ","snp1.3:38.3":"Sevetha pantani senasanani, ","snp1.3:38.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:39.1":"“Mettam upekkham karunam vimuttim, ","snp1.3:39.2":"Asevamano muditanca kale; ","snp1.3:39.3":"Sabbena lokena avirujjhamano, ","snp1.3:39.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:40.1":"“Raganca dosanca pahaya moham, ","snp1.3:40.2":"Sandalayitvana samyojanani; ","snp1.3:40.3":"Asantasam jivitasankhayamhi, ","snp1.3:40.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:41.1":"“Bhajanti sevanti ca karanattha, ","snp1.3:41.2":"Nikkarana dullabha ajja mitta; ","snp1.3:41.3":"Attatthapanna asuci manussa, ","snp1.3:41.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo”. ","snp1.3:41.5":"Khaggavisanasuttam tatiyam. "}